comments: Porter Jr. (HOU) closes out on Herro (MIA) and marginal lower body contact occurs after the release.
Herro's (MIA) right leg drifts out slightly after the release of his jump shot attempt and the contact with Porter Jr. (HOU) is marginal.
Robinson (MIA) grazes Smith Jr.'s (HOU) arm during the rebound and the contact is marginal.
Strus (MIA) legally contests Smith Jr.'s (HOU) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Gordon (HOU) slides his resting hand off of Butler (MIA) as he enters his upward shooting motion and the contact is marginal.
Highsmith (MIA) and Green (HOU) engage and disengage during the rebound and the contact is marginal.
Highsmith (HOU) moves alongside Green's (HOU) path and marginal contact occurs as Green drives into the paint.
Robinson (MIA) jumps from point A to point B and initiates contact with Green (HOU), which affects his driving shot attempt.
Strus (MIA) and Garuba (HOU) come together while pursuing the rebound and the contact is marginal.
Highsmith (MIA) lowers his right arm towards the ball and initiates contact to Garuba's (HOU) head during the layup attempt at the basket.
Robinson (MIA) legally boxes out Smith Jr. (HOU) during the rebounding opportunity.
Strus (MIA) brushes Gordon's (HOU) side as he slips out of the pick and the contact with Gordon is marginal.

Smith Jr. (HOU) beats Butler (MIA) to the spot during the drive and absorbs the marginal contact with the offensive player. Butler (MIA) loses control of his dribble as he spins and falls to the ground.
Herro (MIA) legally contests Gordon's (HOU) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Highsmith (MIA) and Garuba (HOU) reach up for the ball and marginal arm contact occurs during the rebounding opportunity.
Gordon (HOU) gathers the ball on his left foot and hops consecutively on it.
Highsmith's (MIA) hand lightly brushes Garuba's (HOU) side and the contact during the layup attempt is marginal.
Strus (MIA) firms up on his left foot and marginal contact occurs as Porter Jr. (HOU) goes over the pick.
Green (HOU) moves alongside Herro's (MIA) path and marginal body contact occurs during the drive.
Green (HOU) legally contests Herro's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Robinson (MIA) and Smith Jr. (HOU) both initially make contact with the ball and then marginal arm contact occurs as Smith Jr. secures the rebound.
Robinson (MIA) reestablishes position in the court of play prior to coming into contact with the ball.
Garuba (HOU) firms up on his left leg and marginal contact occurs as Herro (MIA) goes over the screen.
Gordon (HOU) and Herro (MIA) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs as the screen is set.
Garuba (HOU) establishes himself in Butler's (MIA) path and Garuba absorbs the marginal contact as the two players come together.
Garuba (HOU) reestablishes himself in Butler's (MIA) path and marginal contact occurs as the players come together during the pick.
Butler (MIA) legally contests Porter Jr.'s (HOU) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Robinson (MIA) is the last player to come into contact with the ball prior to it going out of bounds. Possession should have been retained by Houston.
Garuba (HOU) gets his right hand to the ball and dislodges it from Robinson's (MIA) grasp as Robinson is securing the loose ball.
